fully.\n- {@grass_green}ACC{@DEFAULT}: Chance to hit an enemy is increased. This stat is essential when fighting an enemy with high Evasion.\n- {@green}Effect Resistance{@DEFAULT}: Chance to negate harmful effects from enemies’ skills.\n- {@RED}Effect Accuracy{@DEFAULT}: Decrease enemy\'s chance to resist effect. Can’t decrease Effect Resistance below 15%.',
